    "en": {
      "name": "Snake-Eyes Execute Dragon",
      "effect": "1 Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner monsters\nDuring the Main Phase (Quick Effect): You can target 1 face-up monster on the field or in either GY; place it face-up in its owner's Spell & Trap Zone as a Continuous Spell, also this card cannot use this effect next turn. During the Battle Phase (Quick Effect): You can target 2 cards on the field (1 monster and 1 Continuous Spell); destroy them. You can only use each effect of \"Snake-Eyes Execute Dragon\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
